<a name="FAQ1SEC2" id="#FAQSEC1"></a><FONT FACE="Geneva, Verdana" Size="3"><STRONG>About MindField Group</STRONG></FONT></p>
<ol>
  <li><a name="FAQ1" id="#FAQ1"></a><FONT FACE="Geneva, Verdana" Size="2"><STRONG>What is MindField Group?</STRONG><br />
        MindField Group is Canada's experts in hourly recruiting.  Our corporate Head Office is located near the historic Gastown district of Vancouver, BC.  Visit our website at <a href="http://www.mindfieldgroup.com" target="_blank">www.mindfieldgroup.com</a>.  We see ourselves as your partner in  recruitment.  We act as your  company-branded, fully operational recruitment team that helps you to make  better hires.</font><br /><br />
  </li>
  <li><a name="FAQ2" id="#FAQ2"></a><FONT FACE="Geneva, Verdana" Size="2"><STRONG>How does MindField Group find candidates?</STRONG><br />
        We use various online sources to find job seekers including major national,  provincial, and local job boards, as well as social media networks such as  Facebook.  These online job advertisements are linked to your branded landing page on the web  where applicants then enter to complete the application process.  <BR /><BR />Applicants are pre-screened by MindField Group’s team of Talent Acquisition Specialists against  the job requirements described by your Hiring Manager.  This ensures only the highest-quality and  best-suited candidates are submitted to you for in-person interview.</FONT><br /><br />
  </li>
  <li><a name="FAQ3" id="#FAQ3"></a><FONT FACE="Geneva, Verdana" Size="2"><STRONG>How does MindField Group manage the candidates who apply online?</STRONG></FONT></li>
  <ol>
    <li><FONT FACE="Geneva, Verdana" Size="2">Candidates who apply online are asked to submit their contact details, complete an in-depth  online assessment, and to upload an electronic copy of their resume.</FONT></li>
    <li><FONT FACE="Geneva, Verdana" Size="2">MindField Group’s team of Talent Acquisition Specialists review these materials and contacts  by telephone only those candidates who are best qualified to meet the  requirements provided in the job description.   A phone screen is completed at this time.  </FONT></li>
    <li><FONT FACE="Geneva, Verdana" Size="2">Qualified  candidates are delivered directly to your email inbox.  This email will include the candidate’s  resume, online assessment, and phone screen notes.</FONT></li>
    <li><FONT FACE="Geneva, Verdana" Size="2">All applications and resumes are kept on file electronically with MindField Group  and can be used to fill vacancies with your company as they arise.</FONT><br />
    </li>
  </ol>
  <li><a name="FAQ4" id="#FAQ4"></a><FONT FACE="Geneva, Verdana" Size="2"><STRONG>What is the most efficient method of contacting MindField Group?</STRONG></FONT><BR /><FONT FACE="Geneva, Verdana" Size="2">Within  the HirePortal, use the “Live Chat” feature to speak directly to  MindField Group’s Customer Success Team. “Live Chat” is similar to sending instant messages or telephone text messages in that  communication happens in real time.  Watch a short training video on <strong><a href="http://www.screencast.com/users/MindField/folders/Hiring%20Manager%20Portal%20Training%20Videos/media/cd4a37c5-d174-40c9-a2ee-308a5b17a3f0" target="_BLANK">how to use “Live Chat”</a>.</strong></font><br /><br />
  </li>
  <li><a name="FAQ5" id="#FAQ5"></a><FONT FACE="Geneva, Verdana" Size="2"><STRONG>When should I contact MindField Group?</STRONG><BR />Please contact our Customer Success Team any time you have a recruitment process  question for which you cannot find an answer to within this FAQ document, or  cannot find within the <em>Help</em> section  of the HOURLY Jobs Portal.  Any candidate  quality issues specific to your store location can be addressed via “Live Chat”.</FONT><br /><br />
